Package asypad.ui.command

Package that includes classes to store user commands for implementation of undo/redo features.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColorCommand
    This class represents the action of recoloring a shape.
    Command
    This class stores a user command.
    DeleteCommand
    This class represents a command where a shape is deleted.
    DragCommand
    This class represents a command where a label is repositioned by the user.
    DrawCommand
    This class represents a command where the user draws a shape onto the screen.
    HideCommand
    This class represents a command where shapes are hidden/shown.
    MoveCommand
    This class represents a command where a point is moved by the user.
    RenameCommand
    This class represents a command where a point is renamed.
    StrokeWidthCommand
    This class represents a command where the Stroke Width is updated.

Package asypad.ui.command Description

Package that includes classes to store user commands for implementation of undo/redo features.
